text: Fré Vooys-Bosma (30 September 1926 - 25 April 2020) was a Dutch politician. Vooys-Bosma became the first female Labour Party councilor in The Hague in 1982. She retired in 1990. Fré Vooys-Bosma died in The Hague on 25 April 2020, aged 93. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Aldermen of the Netherlands Category:Dutch councillors Category:Labour Party (Netherlands) politicians Category:Politicians from The Hague
